  "detailed_description": "<h1>Try the demo!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Obsurity swept the whole of Ahn'koval. Eternal darkness and pain is all that we have.<br>Obsurity - Atmospheric action with puzzles and two playable characters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125110/extras/c2e0ec7b254b4d8ccf6cd7dbdee522db.poster.avif?t=1718124874\" width=512 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125110/extras/c2e0ec7b254b4d8ccf6cd7dbdee522db.webm?t=1718124874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125110/extras/c2e0ec7b254b4d8ccf6cd7dbdee522db.mp4?t=1718124874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The story tells about the fate of a knight exile and a young treasure seeker.<br><br>One interconnecting tale of suffering and sacrifice.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><strong>Features</strong><li>A ghoulishly atmospheric, yet beautiful pixel art world.<br></li><li>Many secrets and puzzles<br></li><li>Confused and mysterious plot<br></li><li>Two main characters, each with their own unique gameplay styles<br></li><li>Each pixel is placed with love!</li></ul>",
